nodes.title: Background
widgets_values: The image shows a white wall in the middle of a desert, with the sun shining brightly in the background. The sand is a golden hue, and the wall is a stark contrast to the bright blue sky.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: 360HDR, 360 degree, vr, A seamless panoramic view of a futuristic, ultra-modern bedroom seamlessly integrated into a rocky cave. The room features sleek, curved architecture with smooth dark walls, illuminated by soft ambient lighting embedded into the ceiling and walls. A minimalist, low-profile bed with dark bedding is positioned centrally, surrounded by modern decor. The cave walls form part of the space, blending natural rock with the smooth surfaces. A large, round window reveals a dramatic rocky landscape outside, contrasting with the room's sleek design.

nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: 360HDR, 360 degree, vr, Create a minimalist landscape under a clear blue sky, featuring gently rolling sand dunes in soothing beige tones.
